{% comment %}
  Certificate & Authenticity Page – Vaama
{% endcomment %}

<style>
  .certificate-page {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 20px;
    font-family: inherit;
    color: #2b2b2b;
  }

  .certificate-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .certificate-header h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .certificate-header p {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #555;
  }

  .cert-section {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    margin-top: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .cert-box {
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    padding: 10px 10px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #faf9f7;
  }

  .cert-logo .igi-logo{
    max-width: 100%;
    
  }
    .igi-logo{
        padding:32px;
    }
  .cert-box h2 {
    text-align:center;
    font-size: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .cert-box p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #444;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cert-list {
    padding-left: 18px;
  }

  .cert-list li {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .highlight {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #000;
  }
@media (min-width: 767px) {
    .igi-logo{
        padding:0px;
    }
}
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .cert-section {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}

</style>

<div class="certificate-page">

  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="certificate-header">
    <h1>Certified. Documented. Trusted.</h1>
    <p>
      We craft every Vaama piece with a simple, uncompromising belief: when someone chooses their dream jewellery to celebrate their story, they deserve complete transparency, proven quality, and lasting value.
      <br><br>
      Every design that leaves our workshop carries authenticated details of its gold and diamonds. Not as a formality, but as a promise — that what you wear is exactly what we say it is.
      <br><br>
      Our mission is to build a brand where trust is not claimed, but documented. Our vision is to treat every customer as part of the <span class="highlight">Vaama Family</span>, deserving only the finest we can create.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Certification Sections -->
  <div class="cert-section">

    <!-- SGL -->
    <div class="cert-box">
      <img
        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/WhatsApp_Image_2026-01-29_at_4.19.32_PM_1_2.webp?v=1769686949"
        alt="SGL Certificate"
        class="cert-logo"
      >

      <h2>Certification for Diamonds Below 1 Carat</h2>

      <p>
        For diamonds below 1 carat, each jewellery piece is accompanied by certification from
        <span class="highlight">Solitaire Gemological Laboratories (SGL)</span>.
        This jewellery certificate clearly documents the essential specifications of your piece.
      </p>

      <ul class="cert-list">
        <li>Gold purity (KT)</li>
        <li>Diamond weight</li>
        <li>Gold weight</li>
        <li>Diamond colour</li>
        <li>Diamond clarity</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        This ensures you know the true specifications of your jewellery, with full authenticity
        officially recorded.
      </p>
        <img
        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/WhatsApp_Image_2026-01-29_at_4.19.32_PM_1_1_4.webp?v=1769686949"
        alt="SGL Certificate"
        class="cert-logo"
      >

    </div>

    <!-- IGI -->
    <div class="cert-box">
      <img
        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0634/8239/6854/files/OIP.webp?v=1769689959"
        alt="IGI Certificate"
        class="cert-logo igi-logo"
      >

      <h2>Certification for Diamonds Above 1 Carat (Solitaires)</h2>

      <p>
        Every solitaire above 1 carat is certified by
        <span class="highlight">International Gemological Institute (IGI)</span>,
        one of the world’s most recognised gemological authorities.
      </p>

      <p>Our standards are intentionally selective:</p>

      <ul class="cert-list">
        <li>Only E colour</li>
        <li>VVS2 clarity</li>
        <li>Excellent to Ideal cut proportions and dimensions</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        Out of every 10 diamonds we evaluate, only about 2 pass Vaama’s quality filters.
        This means your solitaire is not just certified — it is chosen from the top tier
        of diamonds available.
      </p>

      <p>
        This is how we ensure that when you choose Vaama, you receive not just jewellery,
        but the best version of it — chosen with care, backed by proof, and delivered with pride.
      </p>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>
